e w czasie rzeczywistym, aby odzyska\u0107 swoj\u0105 pozycj\u0119 sprzed przerwy w dost\u0119pno\u015bci.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, stosuj\u0105c powy\u017csze kroki, zwi\u0119kszysz swoje szanse na udane wznowienie sprzeda\u017cy i skuteczn\u0105 odbudow\u0119 pozycji na rynku.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak skutecznie wznowi\u0107 sprzeda\u017c produktu na Amazonie?<\/h1>\n<p>Czy zdarzy\u0142o Ci si\u0119, \u017ce Tw\u00f3j produkt<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3865,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3864","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3864"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3864"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3864\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3865"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3864"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3864"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3864"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}